Beautifully designed with a bold exterior edged with sportiness here is the perfect outdoor analog watch for women that is made to impress with its appearance that is tinged with subtle resoluteness that will carry into your attire. The watch is apt to team up with your sports gear when you are heading out for a run. Wear this watch to sporting events like a cricket or football match teamed with your favourite teams jersey and be perfectly dressed for the occasion.

Body and Design

This Diesel Analog watch for women comes with a cool contemporary dial that has a width of 36.8 mm a height of 40 mm and a thickness of 11.6 mm. The dial has been set on a stainless steel strap that wears like a bracelet. A stainless steel case encases the dial providing protection to the watch and ensuring its safety. The neat sporty air of the watch is enhanced with a sunray dial.

Functions and Other Features

Water resistant up to a depth of 50 m accessorise your swimwear with a stylish watch when you take a swim that is as great with its functions as you can time your laps and better your workout in efficiency and skill. This watch is sure to appeal to the adventurous with its fashionable exterior and intrinsically quality so wear this watch when you are engaged in white water rafting. Persons involves in non-snorkeling water related work and fishing will be impressed with the quality of this watch in terms of its amazing appearance and its style.
